WEBVTT

00:01.183 --> 00:02.745
Previously on "Mistresses"...

00:03.068 --> 00:05.358
- I thought you were done with Sam.
- I am. It's a schoolboy crush

00:05.358 --> 00:06.426
he's taking a step too far.

00:06.426 --> 00:08.358
Maybe you seduced her.

00:08.358 --> 00:09.926
Sally, Alex and I are just friends.

00:09.926 --> 00:12.795
If you believe that, then
you are dumber than you look.

00:12.795 --> 00:15.098
Congratulations. Savi told me... the baby.

00:16.432 --> 00:18.935
For the first time since
you told me, I feel better.

00:18.935 --> 00:22.338
I saw Paul. I just saw my dead husband.

00:22.338 --> 00:24.841
No, you didn't. Sweetie,
you've gotta let go.

00:28.945 --> 00:30.947
Hi, April.

00:35.885 --> 00:38.221
Hi.

00:38.221 --> 00:40.456
Wh... I don't know who you
are, but this isn't funny.

00:40.456 --> 00:42.458
April, it's me.

00:42.458 --> 00:43.960
It's Paul.

00:43.960 --> 00:45.027
No, you're not Paul.

00:45.027 --> 00:47.330
You can't be Paul. Paul is dead.

00:47.330 --> 00:49.165
- Just take a breath.
- You've been dead for three years.

00:49.165 --> 00:50.933
You... you died. You drowned.

00:50.933 --> 00:52.101
I didn't.

00:52.101 --> 00:53.202
I didn't die.

00:56.005 --> 00:58.074
I faked my death.

01:02.548 --> 01:04.784
Hello? What? Right now?

01:04.784 --> 01:06.318
Oh, my God.

01:06.318 --> 01:09.655
No, of course. Yes. Of course. Okay.

01:09.655 --> 01:13.192
Shh... um, Lucy just
threw up in her carpool.

01:13.192 --> 01:14.260
She's on her way back home right now.

01:14.260 --> 01:15.494
You have to go. You have to get...

01:15.494 --> 01:16.495
I have to talk to you.

01:16.495 --> 01:18.264
You have to get out of here!

01:18.264 --> 01:19.632
Okay. I'm gonna text you my number.

01:19.632 --> 01:22.168
Get in touch with me when you can.

01:29.999 --> 01:31.300
Hi.

01:31.300 --> 01:32.368
Hey.

01:34.703 --> 01:36.672
You look nice.

01:36.672 --> 01:38.474
- I do?
- Yeah.

01:38.474 --> 01:40.542
Thank you.

01:40.542 --> 01:43.479
It's almost noon. Shouldn't you be at work?

01:43.479 --> 01:46.515
Oh, I'm going in late today.

01:46.515 --> 01:48.584
I have a doctor's appointment.

01:48.584 --> 01:50.419
My 6-week checkup.

01:50.419 --> 01:53.455
I wasn't sure if I should tell you.

01:53.455 --> 01:56.358
Uh, but now that you know,

01:56.358 --> 01:59.461
if you'd like to come with me, you can.

01:59.461 --> 02:02.398
Obviously, you don't have to.

02:02.398 --> 02:03.999
No. No. Um,

02:03.999 --> 02:05.401
it's just...

02:05.401 --> 02:07.436
it is a bit late for me
to reschedule my day...

02:07.436 --> 02:08.937
- Yeah.
- But I'll... I'll go to the next one. Okay?

02:08.937 --> 02:11.473
- Okay.
- Okay.

